\pard\ql\li360\sa0\sb0\f2\fs16 \~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~# This is mainly intended for EMG RMS/MPF/MDF summaries:\par
\pard\ql\li360\sa0\sb0\f2\fs16 \~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~# stable enough in frequency, while still tracking time variation.\par
